            <a class="citerefentry" href="glRotate.xml"><span class="citerefentry"><span class="refentrytitle">glRotate</span></span></a>,
            <a class="citerefentry" href="glScale.xml"><span class="citerefentry"><span class="refentrytitle">glScale</span></span></a>
        </p></div><div class="refsect1"><a id="Copyright"></a><h2>Copyright</h2><p>
